name: Transvergent Dreams of the Crossworld Eclipse
description: In this dreamlike scene, phantasmic pareidolia and numinous augurs gather in selenolatry attendance to observe the sign of the eschaton. The lunar crossworld eclipse heralds the enrolment of the unconquered soul, Atummia Mammen, fo fulfil its destiny in wagers of doom and deliverance. 2K image. https://twitter.com/sweventel
